<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ar" dir="rtl">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>RIM_NEX App Store</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --gold-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFD700 0%, #FFA500 100%);
            --metallic-bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #1A1A1A 0%, #2A2A2A 100%);
            --text-gold: #FFD700;
        }
        body {
            background-color: #000000;
            color: #FFFFFF;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            background: var(--gold-gradient);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .subtitle {
            color: #CCCCCC;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .byline {
            color: #FFD700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .status {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #222;
            color: #FFD700;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #FFD700;
        }
        .app-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .app-item {
            background: var(--metallic-bg);
            border: 2px solid #FFD700;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 15px auto;
            padding: 15px;
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 450px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 215, 0, 0.4);
        }
        .app-info {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            color: #FFFFFF;
        }
        .app-info i {
            margin-left: 10px;
            font-size: 1.5em;
            color: #FFD700;
        }
        .install-btn {
            background: var(--gold-gradient);
            color: #000000;
            border: none;
            padding: 10px 25px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 1em;
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .install-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>RIM_NEX</h1>
        </div>
        <p class="subtitle">التطبيقات موقعة بشهادة مجانية</p>
        <p class="byline">بواسطة: RIM_NEX</p>
        <div class="status"><i class="fa-solid fa-eye"></i> الزوار: متصل</div>
        
        <ul class="app-list">
            <li class="app-item">
                <div class="app-info">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-tiktok"></i>
                    <span>تيك توك</span>
                </div>
                <a class="install-btn" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=https://rim-nex.vercel.app/tiktok.plist">تثبيت</a>
            </li>
            <li class="app-item">
                <div class="app-info">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-telegram"></i>
                    <span>تيليجرام</span>
                </div>
                <a class="install-btn" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=https://rim-nex.vercel.app/telegram.plist">تثبيت</a>
            </li>
            <li class="app-item">
                <div class="app-info">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-whatsapp"></i>
                    <span>واتساب</span>
                </div>
                <a class="install-btn" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=https://rim-nex.vercel.app/whatsapp.plist">تثبيت</a>
            </li>
            <li class="app-item">
                <div class="app-info">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-youtube"></i>
                    <span>يوتيوب</span>
                </div>
                <a class="install-btn" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=https://rim-nex.vercel.app/youtube.plist">تثبيت</a>
            </li>
            <li class="app-item">
                <div class="app-info">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-netflix"></i>
                    <span>نتفليكس</span>
                </div>
                <a class="install-btn" href="itms-services://?action=download-manifest&url=https://rim-nex.vercel.app/netflix.plist">تثبيت</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
